# Aria / master-agent — optional configuration.
# Every value below has a sensible default; copy to `.env.local` to override.
# No secrets live here: the `claude` CLI brings its own auth ambiently, and
# per-agent integration tokens are stored at runtime under app/data/ (gitignored).

# ── Workspace ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Absolute path to the folder whose top-level subfolders are your "projects".
# Default: the `workspace/` folder next to this app.
# WORKSPACE_DIR=/absolute/path/to/workspace

# ── Voice (TTS) ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# URL of the Kokoro neural-voice sidecar. `npm run dev` starts it on macOS.
# KOKORO_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8001/speak

# ── Memory ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Model used for memory summarization / flow distillation (a cheap, fast model).
# ARIA_MEMORY_MODEL=claude-haiku-4-5-20251001

# Memory ingestion gate — a finished flow is written to memory only if it had at
# least MIN_STEPS successful steps AND (cost >= MIN_COST_USD OR tokens >= MIN_TOKENS).
# costUsd is a notional CLI estimate (often absent on a subscription), so the token
# floor is an OR-fallback. Raise these to be stricter about what gets remembered.
# ARIA_MEMORIZE_MIN_STEPS=2
# ARIA_MEMORIZE_MIN_COST_USD=0.02
# ARIA_MEMORIZE_MIN_TOKENS=8000

# ── Concurrency ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Max number of agent subprocesses running in parallel.
# ARIA_MAX_PARALLEL=4
